query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('unix')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('backup',
'date',
'dns',
'io-redirection',
'keyboard-shortcuts',
'memory',
'sort',
'system-installation',
'upgrade',
'usb',
'vim',
'virtualbox',
'wildcards',
'windows',
'yum');
